  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377250/extras/34b07e2d03a6a3c8c5eb6e9863726935.avif?t=1763846019\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377250/extras_big/34b07e2d03a6a3c8c5eb6e9863726935.webp?t=1763846019 width=1560 height=306 /></span>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Whimel Academy </i>is a slow-paced time manager set at a fantastical school for witches, wizards, and budding mages. You’ll explore the campus, attend classes in subjects like herbology and potion-making, meet new friends, and maybe find a romantic connection.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377250/extras/b78e1c1fc08033c343aac9bca85af0a5.poster.avif?t=1763846019\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377250/extras/b78e1c1fc08033c343aac9bca85af0a5.webm?t=1763846019\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377250/extras/b78e1c1fc08033c343aac9bca85af0a5.mp4?t=1763846019\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377250/extras/8a97d1227386d987c48b98d494143015.avif?t=1763846019\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377250/extras_big/8a97d1227386d987c48b98d494143015.webp?t=1763846019 width=1560 height=306 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Extracurriculars remain an integral part of life at <i>Whimel Academy. </i>Explore part-time jobs around campus to earn money and stat points towards different specialties. Shelve books in the library, grow new plants in the garden, or conduct research in the astronomy tower to earn money for events around the academy. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your wages can be exchanged for a sweet treat in the dining hall, a new book downtown, or accessories for your dorm, including a record player and a cauldron. If you have a particular specialty–such as potion-making or painting–try selling your wares to fund future projects. As you work, however, be mindful of your energy level; you can take a rest in your dorm when needed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377250/extras/204bbdedb80c233d73c5ea07645ac136.poster.avif?t=1763846019\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377250/extras/204bbdedb80c233d73c5ea07645ac136.webm?t=1763846019\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377250/extras/204bbdedb80c233d73c5ea07645ac136.mp4?t=1763846019\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377250/extras/cbe71a2b8ffa1a6c3ed6679c5d64deef.avif?t=1763846019\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377250/extras_big/cbe71a2b8ffa1a6c3ed6679c5d64deef.webp?t=1763846019 width=1560 height=306 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you grow more accustomed to campus, get to know your fellow students. A diverse set of in-game characters, each with unique interests and personalities, are excited to meet you. Interact with these students to increase your friendship level, creating more opportunities for meaningful conversation. Lifelong friendships and youthful romance are waiting to be discovered at Whimel Academy!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377250/extras/049982e43f71de2d08440dc30f465142.poster.avif?t=1763846019\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377250/extras/049982e43f71de2d08440dc30f465142.webm?t=1763846019\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377250/extras/049982e43f71de2d08440dc30f465142.mp4?t=1763846019\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377250/extras/a3d3b8b01ed0b269e35e9ad29df3a0f0.avif?t=1763846019\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377250/extras_big/a3d3b8b01ed0b269e35e9ad29df3a0f0.webp?t=1763846019 width=1560 height=306 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can freely decorate your avatar, your room, and your beloved  kitty. Collect and decorate to your heart's content to show off your unique taste and personality.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377250/extras/c332974ed87d5c2d9ab2c281b8e327a0.poster.avif?t=1763846019\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377250/extras/c332974ed87d5c2d9ab2c281b8e327a0.webm?t=1763846019\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377250/extras/c332974ed87d5c2d9ab2c281b8e327a0.mp4?t=1763846019\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in a charming fantasy world filled with delightful details, a cozy atmosphere, and slice-of-life experiences that transport players to a magical realm. Stepping into this world would be like coming back to a half-forgotten childhood home. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377250/extras/73b5d399e0480b12c846d7f1e908cd5d.poster.avif?t=1763846019\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377250/extras/73b5d399e0480b12c846d7f1e908cd5d.webm?t=1763846019\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377250/extras/73b5d399e0480b12c846d7f1e908cd5d.mp4?t=1763846019\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377250/extras/5dc7295e5dc1961b027cf8092756fb14.avif?t=1763846019\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377250/extras_big/5dc7295e5dc1961b027cf8092756fb14.webp?t=1763846019 width=1560 height=306 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Specialize in different tracks of magic throughout the game. Different combinations of stats would grant you one of the 30+ endings when you graduate. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377250/extras/c275c3990b7e0acfecaa4eac0f4d8da6.poster.avif?t=1763846019\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377250/extras/c275c3990b7e0acfecaa4eac0f4d8da6.webm?t=1763846019\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377250/extras/c275c3990b7e0acfecaa4eac0f4d8da6.mp4?t=1763846019\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
